# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the united nations applauded the news from burma 's military junta that it had freed political opposition leader and nobel peace laureate aung san suu kyi without condition on monday .
# ::alignments
(a / applaud-01
      :ARG0 (n / nation
            :ARG1-of (u / unite-01))
      :ARG1 (n2 / news
            :source (j / junta
                  :mod (m / military)
                  :poss (c / city
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Burma")))
            :topic (f / free-01
                  :ARG0 j
                  :ARG1 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (p / person
                              :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                                    :ARG1 (o / oppose-01
                                          :ARG1 (p2 / politics))))
                        :op2 (p3 / person
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Aung"
                                    :op2 "San"
                                    :op3 "Suu"
                                    :op4 "Kyi")
                              :mod (l2 / laureate
                                    :mod (p4 / peace))))
                  :ARG1-of (c2 / condition-01
                        :polarity -)
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (m2 / monday)))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok kurdish guerrillas attacked a turkish military convoy with automatic weapons , killing one soldier and wounding eight others , authorities said monday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (a / authority)
      :ARG1 (a2 / attack-01
            :ARG0 (g / guerrilla
                  :mod (e / ethnic-group
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Kurd")))
            :ARG1 (c / convoy
                  :mod (m / military)
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name n
                        :op1 "Turkistan")))
      :instrument (w / weapon
            :mod (a3 / automatic))
      :ARG0-of (c3 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (a4 / and
                  :op1 (k / kill-01
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (s2 / soldier
                              :quant 1))
                  :op2 (w2 / wound-01
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (s3 / soldier
                              :quant 8
                              :mod (o / other)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m2 / monday)))

                  :ARG2 (m2 / mother))
            :ARG0-of (h2 / have-03
                  :ARG1 (a3 / and
                        :op1 (l / life
                              :ARG1-of (h3 / hard-02))
                        :op2 (d / die-01
                              :ARG1-of (h4 / have-degree-91
                                    :ARG2 (h5 / hard-02)

            :age (e / early)))

                                    :op1 "Tibet")))))
